      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/pound-falls-as-weak-uk-growth-underscores-need-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示英国十一月份经济增长低于经济学家的预测，英镑下跌，凸显出进一步降息以刺激经济活动的必要性。]]></description>
